flowchart TD
    Start([User launches App]) --> CheckExisting{Is another instance running?}

    CheckExisting -- Yes --> SendArgs[Send command line arguments to existing instance]
    SendArgs --> Exit([Exit current App])

    CheckExisting -- No --> StartListen[Listen for arguments from future instances]
    StartListen --> RunApp[Run normal App interface]
    RunApp --> Stop([App closed by User])
